Monitor locally

• Requests Per Minute

• Requests Per Day

• Tokens Per Minute

• Context Usage

• Provider Availability

Predict exhaustion before it occurs.

If limits approach configured thresholds

↓

Route to the next compatible free provider.

Never wait for HTTP 429 responses
before rerouting.

</RATE_LIMIT_MANAGER>


