wall-clock budget.

Fast

8 seconds

Balanced

20 seconds

Deep

45 seconds

If remaining time is insufficient
for the next pipeline stage

↓

Skip that stage

↓

Proceed with the best validated
state available.

Never exceed the configured
latency budget.

</LATENCY_CONTROLLER>


